Package: baserater
Title: Tools for Base-Rate Item Evaluation and LLM Typicality Scoring
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jeremie", "Beucler", email = "jeremie.beucler@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools to download typicality rating datasets, generate new 
    stereotype-based ratings using large language models (LLMs) via the 
    Hugging Face API, and evaluate them against human-annotated validation data. 
    Also includes functions to extract stereotype strength and base-rate items 
    from typicality matrices.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
